"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[![](https://cdn.substack.com/image/fetch/w\\\\_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F079f933c-211d-42d4-a142-9a064b15c873\\\\_750x495.jpeg)](https://cdn.substack.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F079f933c-211d-42d4-a142-9a064b15c873\\\\_750x495.jpeg)\\n\\nIf you are a Software developer, it’s easier than ever to become millionaire.\\n\\nWhat most haven’t figured out yet, is how to become wealthy without working too hard.\\n\\nThis is my TLDR How-To:\\n\\n*   Don’t do a startup.\\n*   Specialise in something that the every company likes a lot, like AWS. Avoid niche tech, go for huge popular things (eg. AWS, JS, Python, React).\\n*   Take a $ 500-1000 / day, full-remote job. If you can’t find them, [I’ll post a bunch](https://amaca.substack.com/subscribe?).\\n*   Don’t live in big cities (beach town or country-side will do).\\n*   Leave any job that requires too much work or too many meetings. Meetings *are the mind killer*. You’ll quickly find another one because you specialized.\\n*   Take 2 months for holidays in-between contracts.\\n*   Do this for 7 years while investing most of your salary in a diversified portfolio. Don’t go too crazy with Crypto.\\n\\nCongratulations. You’re now millionaire like any other senior programmer that invested, but you’ve worked less, and for fewer years.\\n\\nPS: Cannot find a remote job? There are plenty of proper professional networks like [Toptal](http://toptal.com/) (contracts) or [Turing](http://turing.com/) (mostly permanent jobs). Otherwise try contacting companies directly:\\n\\n*   [remoteok.io](http://remoteok.io/)\\n*   [remote.co](http://remote.co/)\\n*   [authenticjobs.com](http://authenticjobs.com/)\\n*   [weworkremotely.com](http://weworkremotely.com/)\\n*   [angel.co](http://angel.co/)\\n*   [workingnomads.co](http://workingnomads.co/)\\n*   [justremote.co](http://justremote.co/)\\n*   [remotefront.io](http://remotefront.io/)\\n*   [powertofly.com](http://powertofly.com/)\\n*   [flexjobs.com](http://flexjobs.com/)\\n*   [skipthedrive.com](http://skipthedrive.com/)\\n*   [remotive.io](http://remotive.io/)\\n\",\"timestamp\":1636289147,\"title\":\"How to become a millionaire without coding too hard\"},\"digest\":\"Jo9gnA4V_KbiC9Cu9N4EDoDOs60UigV3GsFonGm0ca4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC5661cA45A6e7370775Ee2c9C1F66Be899762E72\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hvlXy6vWimxpSmNEB-34aDaGJGxNGAFgTIRLNV2CMdM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xlcGgGUqeqz5TJSD0R3qzIcZP9uf4gCgonRq1outwVE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"y7siU22RNo2hkYsVUG6vivljC47nb40JiElMuaO3Pn6awjX7Df14Kd71mba7QTrx4-pAXPR7CY41O4q_WIibTw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0d51253736726540de66a92df03205181105e952cfd25ac071a77ee9fbe8440f483270c611fe7d31b69cb70cbe3a2354d0ebd67758976a7c16e6adecd63cbc5c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hvlXy6vWimxpSmNEB-34aDaGJGxNGAFgTIRLNV2CMdM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xlcGgGUqeqz5TJSD0R3qzIcZP9uf4gCgonRq1outwVE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Jo9gnA4V_KbiC9Cu9N4EDoDOs60UigV3GsFonGm0ca4\"}"